channel.title: Career planning tips for you people who want to be something some day
channel.description:
I found this on w3school today and thought about this myself. I mean seriously..... When I get to college I will be a web programmer or game programmer or possibly both, but I do know one thing; might as well find the right things I'll need for the future now because it will in specific situations so... heres the link:
http://www.w3schools.com/careers/career_tips.asp
Really good even though I scanned through it l0l, the headers pretty much explain the tips :P.
